{
  "texts": [
    "We expect the service providers to tune the system in favor of stability than speed.",
    "Latency budget estimation Our latency (compute) budget estimation currently depends on predicting accurately the client's bandwidth and the data size of the video frames.",
    "With image encoding such as JPEG and PNG, the compressed size depends on the changing content of the image, which affects the estimation of network time.",
    "We plan to explore the more advanced bandwidth estimation techniques and frame/video compression scheme with a constant compression ratio.",
    "Accuracy optimization Jellyfish aims to optimize for accuracy by selecting the best possible DNN variants from the collection (bag) of diverse DNNs for the current system conditions."
  ]
}